<subSubSection pageId="11" pageNumber="800" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="11.[113,650,1135,1256]" box="[113,213,1135,1161]" pageId="11" pageNumber="800">REMARKS</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="11.[113,650,1135,1256]" pageId="11" pageNumber="800">The species is characterized by having deep hydrothecae and by the development of a shallow projection on the adcauline wall of the hydrothecae.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
